    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Bratislava Town Council (Augsburg, 3 April
                    1548)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p>As requested, Oláh has intervened with the King with the articuli that
                            were sent the other day, and he has managed to secure a good offer. They
                            should know that Oláh always represents their interests with
                            benevolence, and he is attaching the King’s response to Gáspár Serédy in
                            the matter they share with him. Mihály Mérey will tell them about the
                            rest of the matters pertaining to them, as well as the King’s
                            response.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p>Prudentes et Circumspecti Domini, Amici nobis Honorandi, salutem et
                    obsequiorum nostrorum commendationem!</p>
                <p>Miseratis nuper cum litteris vestris ad nos articulos quosdam certorum negotiorum
                    vestrorum, rogaveratisque nos per easdem litteras vestras, ut in eisdem
                    articulis apud <persName>regiam maiestatem</persName>, dominum nostrum
                    clementissimum intercederemus, relationemque vobis bonam impetraremus.<note
                        type="critic">See Ep. 682.</note><ref>/o:olahus.tei.15480225_2</ref> Sciatis
                    nos pro nostra in vos benevolentia et studio in eisdem negotiis vestris apud
                    suam maiestatem intercessisse et litteras suae maiestatis ratione<note
                        type="critic">Uncertain reading.</note> negotii, quod cum domino
                        <persName>Gaspare Seredy</persName> commune habetis, ad eundem dominum
                    Seredy datas praesentibus annexas ad vos misisse. De reliquis autem rebus et
                    negotiis vestris, quid sua maiestas responderit, Dominationibus Vestris per
                    egregium dominum <persName>Michaelem Merey</persName><note type="critic">Mihály
                        Mérey.</note> brevi significabimus. </p>
                <p>Dominationes Vestras feliciter valere optamus.</p>
                <p>Datum <placeName>Augustae Vindelicorum</placeName> tertia Aprilis 1548.</p>
                <p>
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus Zagrabiensis
                            cancellarius regiae maiestatis etc. manu propria</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p>Prudentibus et circumspectis dominis iudici et iuratis ceterisque civibus
                    civitatis Posoniensis etc. dominis et amicis nobis honorandis.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
